    <h1>Social Listening</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of monitoring social platforms and online communities for brand mentions, competitor signals, and industry conversations — then <strong>analysing those patterns</strong> to drive strategy, protect reputation, and surface product insights.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
